{
  "title": "Buttery Silky Cacao Dip",
  "description": "A luxurious and creamy cacao dip perfect for solo dinner nights, featuring a rich blend of dairy-free butters and pure chocolate, designed to satisfy the sweet tooth without compromising on health or dietary preferences.",
  "cuisine": "norwegian",
